{"tid":2342483,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［FGO］當我以為自己已經算肝...其實只係0","createTime":"2020-12-27T07:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T10:09:11.000Z","uid":305919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ced5240bf9db3c0dbfb0f719067f7b3874ffc77","tid":2342483,"uid":305919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"有玩FGO嘅人都知依隻遊戲係唔可以跳寶具，唔可以掃蕩，2倍速=正常速度，再加上有無限池依個肝帝專屬活動<br />\n<br />\n利申平時依個活動最少刷200箱，最多300箱<br />\n<br />\n啱啱見到依位用錢去肝嘅肝之財神，我瞬間覺得自己垃圾都不如....<br />\n正常平均一場全+12大約200幾票（好似係冇去計）然後依位神係每次都千幾二次箱，今次仲要3918箱，即係180萬張票+<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家平時係刷幾多箱，定係都已經成神了"},{"pid":"f2832b43bafdf6967586f275227e14ddc84d86f7","tid":2342483,"uid":305919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eU7jOgM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeU7jOgM.png&h=0319afab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zPrgQu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzPrgQu7.jpg&h=b618472f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e81ca64ecff10631cd8c5351e263600ca81504f","tid":2342483,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T10:09:11.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}